| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3334 — Recovery Inhibition (shinyhunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 830e9ea7-b76e-5c7c-b0ac-1bc81cbea1b4"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
